      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>pomegranate molasses</strong> and <strong>agave nectar</strong> with the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lime</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>pomegranate dressing </strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
