    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>cauliflower</strong> into florets </p>\n<p>Add the <strong>cauliflower florets</strong> to a baking tray, drizzle with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </strong></span><strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong></p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 15-20 min or until tender and golden</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
